invalid type: string "+ Slide 19 \n+ Slide 20 \n+ Slide 21 \n+ Slide 22 \n+ 10. GODAVARI : Godavari breed is a result of crossing of native buffaloes with Murrah bulls.Home tract :\u{f03d} Along the bank of Godavari and Krishna deltaic areas of Karnataka and Andhra Pradesh. Physical Characteristics :\u{f03d} The breed has attained uniformity and almost reached the production level of Murrah."ool. 